I had a similar issue, the first time I tried importing tensorflow I got:
AttributeError: NewBase is_abstract, ImportError: ...
And starting the second time I got the above mentioned error. What solved the issue for me is to update the version of 'six' as instructed in
#1965

Cheers

body:
I had a similar issue, the first time I tried importing tensorflow I got:
AttributeError: NewBase is_abstract, ImportError: ...
And starting the second time I got the above mentioned error. What solved the issue for me is to update the version of 'six' as instructed in 
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/1965

Cheers
